<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span><span class="c5">الْفَصْلُ الثَّانِي:</span> فِي الْأَحْكَامِ ٢٥<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span><span class="c5">الْبَحْثُ الْأَوَّلُ:</span> فِي الحكم ٢٥<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span><span class="c5">البحث الثاني:</span> في الحاكم ٢٨<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span><span class="c5">البحث الثالث:</span> في المحكوم به ٣١<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span><span class="c5">الْبَحْثُ الرَّابِعُ:</span> فِي الْمَحْكُومِ عَلَيْهِ وَهُوَ الْمُكَلَّفُ ٣٦<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span><span class="c5">الْفَصْلُ الثَّالِثُ:</span> فِي الْمَبَادِئِ اللُّغَوِيَّةِ ٤٠<a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
